en_264874_0	A awareness programme for troops at the Security Force Headquarters - Jaffna (SFHQ-J) on ‘Heart Attacks and Prevention’ was conducted by Dr Rajeewa Peiris, Senior Consultant Cardiothoracic Surgeon on Monday (6).
en_264874_1	The programme was conducted under the guidance of Major General Darshana Hettiarachchi, Commander, Security Forces - Jaffna.
en_264874_2	The visiting Senior Consultant educated the gathering on smoking, its effects and preventive measures.
en_264874_3	General Officers Commanding, Brigade Commanders, Battalion Commanders, Officers and Other Ranks took part in the educative programme.
